org.mxupdate.plugin
Class GetProperties_mxJPO

java.lang.Object
  org.mxupdate.plugin.AbstractPlugin_mxJPO
      org.mxupdate.plugin.GetProperties_mxJPO

public class GetProperties_mxJPO
extends AbstractPlugin_mxJPO

The JPO class returns the plug-in properties stored in MX. The JPO returns the in MX stored plug-in properties as string. The plug-in properties was prepared from InstallDataModel_mxJPO.makePluginProperty(org.mxupdate.update.util.ParameterCache_mxJPO,File) while the data model was installed.
The key of the properties are defined in this format:

property keydescription
[TypeDefName].FilePrefixfile prefix
[TypeDefName].FileSuffixfile suffix
[TypeDefName].IconMime64 encoded Gif image
[TypeDefName] is the name of the type definition specified in the mapping properties.
